    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I've taken good care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin. You're going to love how it handles!",
