    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that perfectly balances performance with practicality. The exterior retains a deep, impressive gloss, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is remarkably preserved; the upholstery is firm, the carpets are clean, and the dashboard remains free of sun damage or cracks. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a quiet, responsive engine that provides a confident driving experience. All onboard electronics, from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control, are fully functional. This is a dependable, turn-key vehicle that has been cared for by an owner who values longevity and detail.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
