    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it has been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It drives smoothly and looks great, making it a perfect pick if you're looking for quality without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m super easy to work with, so feel free to message me with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
